    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning enthusiast. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes, and has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium hand-stitched leather remains supple and taut, showing no signs of wear or bolster compression. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized centers with a comprehensive history of preventative maintenance, ensuring the engine and transmission operate with seamless power and refinement. The undercarriage is exceptionally clean, and the original alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. This is a turn-key masterpiece that looks, smells, and drives as if it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
